  "detailed_description": "Here Goes Muffin is an exploratory, physics-based, puzzle platformer, starring... A muffin. With legs. Collect various sweets that will enable you to explore the world in new and exciting ways!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerups</h2> Every powerup gives you a new way to move through the world. For example: <br><br><br><u>The Popsicle Lets You Jump!</u> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/3ebecd3d8a11f4cecbf82cdd8d008304.poster.avif?t=1737749218\" width=394 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/3ebecd3d8a11f4cecbf82cdd8d008304.webm?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/3ebecd3d8a11f4cecbf82cdd8d008304.mp4?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>The Lollipop Wheels let you climb hills, and hang below platforms!</u> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/7063098683c035be7a7bb42802ac57a2.poster.avif?t=1737749218\" width=464 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/7063098683c035be7a7bb42802ac57a2.webm?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/7063098683c035be7a7bb42802ac57a2.mp4?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/967961c648bc54a3c2c893b287a2de85.poster.avif?t=1737749218\" width=468 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/967961c648bc54a3c2c893b287a2de85.webm?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/967961c648bc54a3c2c893b287a2de85.mp4?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And many more! Mix and match your powerups to overcome the unique challenges that come your way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The world</h2> Muffin beware: This place isn't all sugar and sunshine. The path of a muffin is wrought with danger, and soon enough, you will just want to get back home. <br><br>There are several areas to explore; Some cheerful, some inhospitable, and some downright scary ones! All part of one big, interconnected world. <br><br>Jump, climb, swim, and fly your way to new heights (or depths) to see all that the world has to offer, and try not to fall into the many pits of spikes!",
  "about_the_game": "Here Goes Muffin is an exploratory, physics-based, puzzle platformer, starring... A muffin. With legs. Collect various sweets that will enable you to explore the world in new and exciting ways!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerups</h2> Every powerup gives you a new way to move through the world. For example: <br><br><br><u>The Popsicle Lets You Jump!</u> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/3ebecd3d8a11f4cecbf82cdd8d008304.poster.avif?t=1737749218\" width=394 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/3ebecd3d8a11f4cecbf82cdd8d008304.webm?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/3ebecd3d8a11f4cecbf82cdd8d008304.mp4?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>The Lollipop Wheels let you climb hills, and hang below platforms!</u> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/7063098683c035be7a7bb42802ac57a2.poster.avif?t=1737749218\" width=464 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/7063098683c035be7a7bb42802ac57a2.webm?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/7063098683c035be7a7bb42802ac57a2.mp4?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/967961c648bc54a3c2c893b287a2de85.poster.avif?t=1737749218\" width=468 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/967961c648bc54a3c2c893b287a2de85.webm?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550110/extras/967961c648bc54a3c2c893b287a2de85.mp4?t=1737749218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And many more! Mix and match your powerups to overcome the unique challenges that come your way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The world</h2> Muffin beware: This place isn't all sugar and sunshine. The path of a muffin is wrought with danger, and soon enough, you will just want to get back home. <br><br>There are several areas to explore; Some cheerful, some inhospitable, and some downright scary ones! All part of one big, interconnected world. <br><br>Jump, climb, swim, and fly your way to new heights (or depths) to see all that the world has to offer, and try not to fall into the many pits of spikes!",
